Subject: Buses By The Depot + Blowout Sale - Oct 4

A reminder that Buses By The Depot and the annual Bus Depot Garage Sale are
just 2 weeks away - Saturday Oct. 4.  The location is scenic Green Lane Park
in Pennsylvania, around the corner from the Bus Depot. You can camp
overnight or just come for the day. There will be a caravan to the Depot for
our annual clearance sale, followed by pot luck dinner.  

If you want to stay overnight, there is a $10 fee for camping, which you
must pay in advance via Paypal.  See the below link for payment info, and
more info on the event:

http://busdepot.com/BBD2008.htm

